{"tid":775771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］比中介公司走數","createTime":"2018-08-11T12:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T10:08:28.000Z","uid":18577,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f019d268d4dd688719f71ef295e7c7955028d074","tid":775771,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"話說年幾之前我經婚展book左間韓國studio 影pw<br />\n因為上網搵過資料見佢香港..台灣同韓國都有分店..網上都幾多好評..所以都落左訂<br />\n之後臨出發前重上左去佢地分店道比埋尾數<br />\n去到韓國影..佢地服務都幾好..之後一星期左右已經收返原相..因為我係包左50張photoshop (30張係原裝studio PS..另外果廿張就佢另外搵公司PS) 另外搵公司個堆好快就比返我睇..但真係修得好差..連叫佢P走條燈柱都做唔到..之後都諗住算..我另外比錢人p個d就算..因為叫佢整既野基本上都做唔到<br />\n之後有催佢studio ps個d幾時有..佢話未咁快要7月<br />\n好啦..我見8月都黎..就問佢地重未收到..wtsapp又無人覆..之後再問多幾問<br />\n岩岩打電話黎講..老闆資金周轉唔黎..所以未比尾數studio..所以佢地個邊hold住唔比相<br />\n之後再google 下發現原來好多人都比佢地拖住<br />\n而佢地香港同台灣分店都執哂<br />\n我可以點做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">間仆街叫Jun6 </span></span>"},{"pid":"33bbbde53ab9abe99e4b30796fc8ae303ba6a46e","tid":775771,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724e78b1693d571645712ad09dcb9a9c31a87ade","tid":775771,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f5b6d11b5ccef584d70dfacf370fe4ff405561","tid":775771,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"查唔到"},{"pid":"de61b6e688b23369c29e04237f716e0034209ace","tid":775771,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37f5b6d11b5ccef584d70dfacf370fe4ff405561","tid":775771,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"查唔到"},"citedBy":0,"r